title: File:Ceremony for the future submarine USS Baltimore while aboard the USS Constellation in Baltimore, Maryland on September 20, 2024 - 18.jpg
author: U.S. Deputy Secretary of Defense Kathleen H. Hicks
description: Deputy Secretary of Defense Kathleen H. Hicks speaks during the naming ceremony for the future submarine USS Baltimore while aboard the USS Constellation in Baltimore, Md. Sept. 20, 2024.  Hicks accepted the offer of becoming the sub’s sponsor from Secretary of the Navy Carlos Del Toro. (DoD photo by EJ Hersom)
